SUBSTITUTE FOR
HOUSE BILL NO. 5724
A bill to amend 1939 PA 288, entitled
"Probate code of 1939,"
(MCL 710.21 to 712B.41) by adding section 18u to chapter XIIA.
THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF MICHIGAN ENACT:
1 CHAPTER XIIA
2 Sec. 18u. If a court-ordered treatment plan includes referring
3 a child to placement in a residential treatment program, the
4 department shall ensure that the child is placed with a residential
5 treatment program that has an adequate array of beds not more than
6 14 days after the referral.
